title: TFT
body: To game einai xalia aparadekto kai imiteles....poli kaki douleia opws mas exete sinithisei xronia twra kai tou dinw 0 sta 10 opws olo genika to game dioti einai oti xeirotero ....eseis blepete na kanete ena champ OP kai otan to kanete auto einai se thesi na polemaei 1v9 (shyvana-draven) episeis mou exete balei ta spasmena buffs (noble-yordle-glacial-shapeshifters) pou exw barethei ti zwi mou na ta blepw se kathe game me ta opoia aneta pas challenger se 10 meres to poli ....afiste loipon ta kainourgia pragmata kai kante to palio kalo lol swsto gt exoume barethei me tin politiki sas...alore
